data.description: Discover your dream home nestled in Coon Rapids – a spacious rambler boasting an expansive fenced lot, offering tranquility in a vibrant neighborhood. Embrace convenience with proximity to the light rail, shopping centers, and esteemed schools. Inside, be greeted by hardwood floors adorning the main level, featuring 4 inviting bedrooms for your comfort. The lower level, a canvas awaiting your creativity, presents endless possibilities. Seize this golden chance to personalize and enhance your space, effortlessly building equity with minor cosmetic touches. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to craft your perfect sanctuary.
